sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant API as Orchestrator API<br/>8033/TCP HTTP
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GenGRPC as TGIS / Caikit NLP<br/>8033|8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI API (vLLM)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Text Generation with Input/Output Detection (Unary)

    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/text/generation-detection<br/>HTTP, TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>OTLP: Trace span (start)
    API->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional, Bearer optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked text
    API->>Detector: Detect input content (parallel)<br/>HTTP POST /api/v1/text/contents, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Input detection results
    Note over API: Check input thresholds<br/>Block if harmful detected
    API->>GenGRPC: Generate text<br/>gRPC Generate, mTLS optional
    GenGRPC-->>API: Generated text
    API->>Chunker: Chunk output text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked output
    API->>Detector: Detect output content (parallel)<br/>HTTP POST /api/v1/text/generation, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Output detection results
    Note over API: Check output thresholds<br/>Filter if harmful detected
    API-->>Client: Generation response<br/>(with detection metadata)
    API->>OTLP: Trace span (end)

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection (Streaming)

    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP, TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>Detector: Detect input (text_contents)<br/>HTTP POST, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Input content results
    API->>Detector: Detect input (text_chat)<br/>HTTP POST, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Input chat results
    Note over API: Check input thresholds
    API->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (stream=true)<br/>HTTP/SSE, TLS optional, Bearer optional
    loop Streaming chunks
        OpenAI-->>API: SSE chunk
        API->>Chunker: BidiStreaming chunk<br/>gRPC bidi-stream, mTLS optional
        Chunker-->>API: Tokenized chunk
        API->>Detector: Detect output chunk<br/>HTTP POST, TLS optional
        Detector-->>API: Chunk detection result
        Note over API: DetectionBatcher<br/>aggregates + orders results
        API-->>Client: SSE chunk (filtered)
    end
    API-->>Client: SSE [DONE]

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection

    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>HTTP, TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>Chunker: Chunk text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked text
    API->>Detector: Detect content (parallel)<br/>HTTP POST, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Detection results
    API-->>Client: Detection response

    Note over Client,Health: Health Check Flow

    Client->>Health: GET /health (liveness)<br/>HTTP 8034/TCP
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK (name + version)
    Client->>Health: GET /info (readiness)<br/>HTTP 8034/TCP
    Health->>GenGRPC: Health probe (gRPC/HTTP)
    Health->>Chunker: Health probe (gRPC)
    Health->>Detector: Health probe (HTTP GET /health)
    Health->>OpenAI: Health probe (HTTP GET /health)
    GenGRPC-->>Health: Status
    Chunker-->>Health: Status
    Detector-->>Health: Status
    OpenAI-->>Health: Status
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK (aggregated status)
